author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-PEM FY Net Profit Down At 5.3 Mln Zlotys, Allots 7.7 Mln Zlotys For Dividends
text:
March 28 (Reuters) - PRIVATE EQUITY MANAGERS SA:
* FY NET PROFIT 5.3 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 14.0 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* FY REVENUE 47.7 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 44.1 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* RECOMMENDS TO SPEND IN TOTAL 7.7 MILLION ZLOTYS FOR 2017 DIVIDEND PAYMENT BY USING 2.3 MILLION ZLOTYS OF COMPANYâ€™S SUPPLEMENTARY CAPITAL CREATED FROM UNDISTRIBUTED PROFITS FROM PREVIOUS YEARS
